<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TikLeap Crawler Pro - History</title>

    <!-- Dependencies & Fonts -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="subpages.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="scroll-progress"></div>
    <header>
        <a href="tikleapcrawler.html" class="back-button">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> ZURÜCK
        </a>
        <div data-aos="zoom-out">
            <h1 class="gradient-text hero-title-large"><span class="text-gradient">Changelog</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle-muted">Evolution of the TikLeap Ecosystem</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="glass">
            <span class="version-tag">LATEST - v2.0.8</span>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">✨ <span class="text-gradient">UI/UX Overhaul & Branding</span></h3>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Enterprise Dark-UI:</b> Umstellung auf CTKMessagebox Modals.</li>
                <li><b>Custom Branding:</b> Neues App-Icon & Sidebar Logo.</li>
                <li><b>Crawl Summary:</b> Detaillierter Abschlussbericht nach jedem Run.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass">
            <span class="version-tag">v2.0.7 - v2.0.5</span>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">🛡️ Security & Teams</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Force Proxy Mode:</b> Vollständige Unterbindung der lokalen IP.</li>
                <li><b>Team-Gruppen:</b> Aggregierte Ansichten in Dashboard & Stats.</li>
                <li><b>Realtime Updates:</b> Signal-basiertes Proxy-Monitoring.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass">
            <span class="version-tag">v2.0.0</span>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">🚀 The Big Engine Update</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Modern GUI:</b> Framework-Wechsel auf CustomTkinter.</li>
                <li><b>Engine Switch:</b> Von Selenium auf blitzschnelles curl_cffi.</li>
                <li><b>Auto-Pilot:</b> Planbare Crawler-Rhythmen & System Tray.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass" style="text-align: center;">
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">Vollständiges Changelog auf GitHub verfügbar.</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/Furby87/TikleapCrawler/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md" target="_blank"
                class="bot-link">VIEW FULL CHANGELOG</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>

    <a href="#" class="back-to-top">↑</a>
    <div id="global-footer" data-type="tikleap"></div>
    <script src="config.js"></script>
    <script src="components.js"></script>
</body>

</html>